'''''Jock ya Bushveld,''''' ni filimi yasohotse muri 1986  [[Afurika y’Epfo|yo muri Afurika y'Epfo]]  iyoborwa na  Gray Hofmeyr itunganywa amashusho na  Duncan MacNeillie hamwe na  Duncan MacNeillie Production na Toron International. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Jonathan Rands, Jocelyn Broderick na Michael Brunner mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Gordon Mulholland, Wilson Dunster mu nshingano zunganira n'imbwa "Umfubu. " 

Iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cyanditswe n'umwanditsi wo muri Irilande James Percy FitzPatrick wagiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo mu myaka ya 1800 kandi akibonera ibintu byinshi byabereye mu mashyamba. 

== Umugambi ==
Mu 1886, Percy Fitzpatrick w'imyaka 20 ukomoka mu mujyi wa Cape Town yerekeje ku kirwa cya Delagoa muri Transvaal gucukura zahabu. Agezeyo, abuza icyana cy'imbwa, Jock, kurohama arakirera. Iyo amaherezo Percy ageze iyo yerekeza, nta zahabu iba ikiriho, nuko atangira kuba umuyobozi. Nyuma yaho, we na Jock babayeho mubyabaye byinshi birimo inyamaswa zo mwishyamba hamwe nabashoferi batwaraga abacakara.  

